Key Match Events: Captain Vincent Aboubakar scored a penalty to open the scoring
Martin Hongla scored from the edge of the box
Michael Olunga scored a consolation goal for Kenya
Bryan Mbeumo and Christian Bassogog added more goals for Cameroon
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the heaviest defeat for Harambee Stars under coach Engin Firat
Others: The match took place in Yaounde, Cameroon
